    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan with the <strong>garlic oil</strong> to a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped basa</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked through</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
