    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the basa is cooking, zest<strong> half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>(try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>non-zested lemon</strong> into wedges and reserve for garnish</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
